&lt;p id=&quot;p-rc_41a121af269dd30a-58&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;12,4,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;12,4,0,0&quot;&gt;Manage catering for team meetings and events, and ensure kitchen and office supplies are fully stocked and organized.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
